Redesign city layout around the road: open north gate, no building in the path

The road enters from the north, but the entrance/kiosks/spawn were at the south
with a tower at north-centre — so a building sat dead in the road. Reoriented the
whole city toward the road:
- North edge is now an OPEN gate (two pillars + sign arch) the main street runs
  straight through. Ohio Plaza moved to the south backdrop.
- Skyline frames only the E/W/S edges.
- Kiosks line the entrance avenue just inside the gate; arena in the centre with
  its title pillar at the far (south) end.
- Spawn + travel-home pads sit just inside the gate, facing into the arena.

